item.description: About Me def welcome(): print("Hello! This is Jensen Zhang!") return 😊 Welcome to visit my homepage! I am a senior student in the Department of Computer Science and Technology, Anhui Agricultural University, and I will graduate from college at the end of June this year. In October 2020, I got the opportunity to study for a master’s degree without an examination. This September, I will enter Hefei University of Technology to continue my studies.
